buildspecOverride:
version: 0.2

phases:
  pre_build:
    commands:
      - echo Current directory is $PWD
      - echo CODEBUILD_SRC_DIR is $CODEBUILD_SRC_DIR
      - echo Listing root directory
      - ls -la
      - echo Listing parent directory
      - ls -la ..
      - echo Finding Dockerfile
      - find . -name Dockerfile -type f
      - echo Finding buildspec.yml
      - find . -name buildspec.yml -type f
  build:
    commands:
      - echo Skipping build for debug
